    <string name="about_description">Git Tracker is a standalone, Android application designed to track GitHub repository updates using the public GitHub REST API. By leveraging OkHttp Native ETag Caching and WorkManager with Jitter, it ensures minimal API rate limit usage and maximum battery preservation.</string>
    <string name="key_features">Architecture &amp; Strategy</string>
    <string name="features_list">• Standalone &amp; Offline-first architectural design.\n• OkHttp Native ETag Caching for efficient data sync.\n• WorkManager with Jitter (Flex Intervals) for battery preservation.\n• Automated background update checks and notifications.\n• Modern Jetpack Compose UI with adaptive layouts.</string>
